&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;I&gt;airly2000 &lt;airly2002@...&gt;&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/B&gt; wrote:&lt;/DIV&gt;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE style=&quot;PADDING-LEFT: 5px; MARGIN-LEFT: 5px; BORDER-LEFT: #1010ff 2px solid&quot;&gt;&lt;TT&gt;Elita:&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Elita attempted to catch one of Daddy&#39;s hadns. Soon she&#39;d feel &lt;BR&gt;hungry and tired, but she liked to play a while more with her dad.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, &quot;Nic&quot; &lt;Proudwing500k@h...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Yggdrasil: We&#39;re still discussing details, but I&#39;ll report back &lt;BR&gt;very&lt;BR&gt;&gt; soon. Prime out.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; He frowned in a way that was very similar as that of his infamous&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Autobot ancestor. Kup&#39;s team was good, but it exposed them too &lt;BR&gt;much,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; he thought.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; Yggdrasil: I don&#39;t like the idea that all three highest officers &lt;BR&gt;here,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; meaning you, Rodimus and me, get to go. It will be a drawback if &lt;BR&gt;the&lt;BR&gt;&gt; preds decide to move out just then. I suggest that Rodimus stays &lt;BR&gt;and&lt;BR&gt;&gt; that we replace him with either Empath or Blackfang, or even one of&lt;BR&gt;&gt; the new guys around.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@y...&gt; &lt;BR&gt;wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : :&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Rodimus holds her close, tickling her, while he takes care of &lt;BR&gt;business.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; He opens a comm.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: Yggdrasil, what&#39;s the status of that team?&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Airshadow Nightstar &lt;airly2002@h...&gt; wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Elita:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; Elita continued giggling and laughting. She was enjoying a lot&lt;BR&gt;&gt; playing with her daddy. She was having a lot fun and if she would &lt;BR&gt;be a&lt;BR&gt;&gt; little older, she would have wished that it never ends.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt;Reply-To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;Subject: Re: Daddy &gt;Date: Sat, 10 May 2003 21:59:17 -0700 (PDT) &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt;:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; : Rodimus Prime : : &gt;Rodimus was having fun playing with his &lt;BR&gt;daughter,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; but his thoughts started to dwell on Nightlight. He wished she was&lt;BR&gt;&gt; there so they could all be together as a family. &gt; &gt;Rodimus tossed&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Elita up just a little bit, then cought her. &gt; &gt; &gt;Airshadow &lt;BR&gt;Nightstar&lt;BR&gt;&gt; wrote: &gt;Elita: &gt; &gt;Elita Laughtes Aloud, that was such fun. She was&lt;BR&gt;&gt; gigglig pleaced while she spread her little arms toward her dad &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;From: Richard Allen &gt;Reply-To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;To:&lt;BR&gt;&gt; nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com &gt;Subject: Re: Daddy &gt;Date: Sat, 10 May 2003&lt;BR&gt;&gt; 21:27:31 -0700 (PDT) &gt; &gt;: : Rodimus Prime : : &gt;Rodimus looks &lt;BR&gt;stunned&lt;BR&gt;&gt; after getting hit in the nose. &gt; &gt;Rodimus Prime: I got your hand, &lt;BR&gt;but&lt;BR&gt;&gt; you got daddy&#39;s nose. &gt; &gt;Rodimus raises her over his head and spins&lt;BR&gt;&gt; around twice. &gt; &gt; &gt;airly2000 wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt;Elita laughted more &lt;BR&gt;and&lt;BR&gt;&gt; without liked with her jerking movement she &gt;struck slighty her&lt;BR&gt;&gt; daddy&#39;s nose &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;wrote: &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; Rodimus traps two of her &lt;BR&gt;fingers&lt;BR&gt;&gt; in his mouth, playing around. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: I got your &lt;BR&gt;hand,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; what&#39;cha gunna do? &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; airly2000 wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Elita&lt;BR&gt;&gt; giggled a lot, she touched with one of her little hand his &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;daddy&#39;s&lt;BR&gt;&gt; chin. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; --- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, &lt;BR&gt;Richard&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Allen &gt;wrote: &gt; &gt; &gt; : : Rodimus Prime : : &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus picks up &lt;BR&gt;his&lt;BR&gt;&gt; daughter, holding her close. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: I can tell&lt;BR&gt;&gt; that you are going to be a strong girl. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; airly2000&lt;BR&gt;&gt; wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Eliata laughted and giggled more she &lt;BR&gt;spread&lt;BR&gt;&gt; her little arms &gt;towards &gt; &gt; &gt; her daddy. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; --- In&lt;BR&gt;&gt; nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, Richard Allen &gt; &gt; wrote: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; : : &lt;BR&gt;Rodimus&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Prime : : &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus looked at his fully transformed &lt;BR&gt;daughter. He&lt;BR&gt;&gt; could see &gt; &gt; the &gt; &gt; &gt; influences from Nightlight and himself. &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Rodimus Prime: Now you see your true form hunny. You are &lt;BR&gt;a &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt; &gt; cybertroian transformer. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; airly2000&lt;BR&gt;&gt; wrote:Elita: &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; Elita started to laught more and more.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Sometimes, by seconds, &gt; &gt; &gt; seemed &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; that her little chest&lt;BR&gt;&gt; would open to show the rest of her robot &gt; &gt; &gt; mode. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; At &lt;BR&gt;last,&lt;BR&gt;&gt; that help her to complete her tranform. &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; She looked&lt;BR&gt;&gt; extraordinary like her mommy, but with several &gt;things &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; that&lt;BR&gt;&gt; she heired from her daddy: Her metallic skin was like &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; Nightlight&#39;s, her robot mode mixed Golden, red and copper. Her &gt; &gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; helmet was like Rodim